title: I Am With You In This War
description:
Kirk Minihane is headed to Rough n Rowdy after Cupcake confirms that she needs him in her corner next Friday. Dave Portnoy is nervous about what Kirk will do at the event. Mike reacts to Justin quitting the show & much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
